                        <seg type="rubrication">Holy names; name of the protagonist; names of the
                           donors and the scribe; groups of lines (alternating with black lines) on
                           the incipit page of Text I; incipit of Text II; incipits of
                           sections/miracles of Texts I and II; elements of the punctuation signs;
                           elements of Ethiopic numerals.</seg>
